OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F429A1779879767
OL,3,CEFL confirm play-off final will take
OL,4,Cplace on Saturday despite 'spygate'
OL,5,Cappeal
OL,7,FThe EFL have confirmed the
OL,8,FChampionship play-off final will take
OL,9,Fplace this Saturday (23 May) despite
OL,10,FSouthampton appealing against their
OL,11,Fexpulsion.
OL,13,FThe Saints have been replaced by
OL,14,FMiddlesbrough for the Wembley
OL,15,Fshowpiece against Hull City after they
OL,16,Fadmitted spying on Boro in the build-
OL,17,Fup to the semi-final.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/4
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,430,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F429A1779879767
OL,3,CEFL confirm play-off final will take
OL,4,Cplace on Saturday despite 'spygate'
OL,5,Cappeal
OL,7,FThe club have also been given a four-
OL,8,Fpoint deduction for next season after
OL,9,Fthey also admitted spying on Oxford
OL,10,FUnited and Ipswich Town over the
OL,11,Fcourse of this Championship campaign.
OL,13,FSouthampton have appealed the decision
OL,14,Fmade by the EFL's Independent
OL,15,FDisciplinary Commission with an
OL,16,Foutcome expected to be announced today
OL,17,F(20 May).
OL,19,FBut the EFL had confirmed the game
OL,20,Fwill go ahead regardless of whether
OL,21,Fthe appeal is successful or not.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/4
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,430,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F429A1779879767
OL,3,CEFL confirm play-off final will take
OL,4,Cplace on Saturday despite 'spygate'
OL,5,Cappeal
OL,7,FShould the tie remain between
OL,8,FMiddlesbrough and Hull, the game will
OL,9,Fkick off at 3.30pm but this will be at
OL,10,Fthe later time of 4.30pm should
OL,11,FSouthampton be reinstated.
OL,13,FThe announcement means Hull supporters
OL,14,Fwill be able to make travel plans with
OL,15,Fmore confidence, while Middlesbrough
OL,16,Fand Southampton may have to await the
OL,17,Foutcome of the Saints' appeal.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/4
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
