OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F429A1779879767
OL,3,CEFL confirm play-off final will take
OL,4,Cplace on Saturday despite 'spygate'
OL,5,Cappeal
OL,7,FThe play-off final is considered to be
OL,8,Fthe richest game in world football,
OL,9,Fwith the winners guaranteed a minimum
OL,10,Fof #110m in Premier League broadcast
OL,11,Frevenue.
OL,13,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,14,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,15,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,16,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,17,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,18,Fbelow...
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/4
